sequenceDiagram
    participant Task as 后台任务
    participant State as 任务状态
    participant Ink as Ink 渲染器
    participant Terminal as 终端

    Task->>State: 更新进度 (progress: 50%)
    State->>Ink: 触发重渲染
    Ink->>Terminal: 增量更新进度条

    Note over Task,Terminal: ❌ 错误做法
    Task--xTerminal: 直接 process.stdout.write()
    Note over Task,Terminal: 会破坏 Ink 的渲染状态
